 A Freelancer","subtitle":"AKA, F*** You, Pay Me","tags":["Freelance"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/def91/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/df91e/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.jpg 131w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/9a46b/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.jpg 263w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/def91/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.jpg 525w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/2437e/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.jpg 1050w","sizes":"(min-width: 525px) 525px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/1b701/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.webp 131w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/90103/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.webp 263w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/a7b62/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.webp 525w,\n/static/a2a556c27a6ffd382ddc218a951c59d3/25270/adam-nir-wTO6MWpMrJk-unsplash.webp 1050w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 525px) 525px, 100vw"}]},"width":525,"height":350}}}}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}